</unordered_list>
<text><loc_66><loc_170><loc_451><loc_196>As such, it shall be reiterated that only passers/eligible of the NQESH, Principals Test; or other school head assessment(s) that may s0 be required in the future, shall be eligible for first appointment to School Principal positions.</text>
