<list_item><loc_64><loc_208><loc_450><loc_249>Duly approved appointments shall be announced a day after the issuance of the appointment through the posting of a Notice of Appointments Issued (NAI) in the bulletin boards and through other modes such as, but not limited the DepEd website, office website, or other official social media accounts. The NAI shall remain posted for at least 15 calendar days following such posting: to,</list_item>
