<list_item><loc_65><loc_283><loc_449><loc_339>The cancellation of the appointment shall be reported by the HRMO to the CSC for record purposes. The position is automatically deemed vacant upon cancellation of the appointment by the appointing officer / authority without the need for approval or declaration by the Commission. The HRMPSB may redeliberate, and the appointing officer / authority may select from among the remaining top-ranking candidates for the position or order the re-publication of the vacant position pursuant to RA No. 7041.</list_item>
<list_item><loc_64><loc_344><loc_449><loc_376>34_ or employees who are on official leave of absence, training or scholarship grant; whose appointment shall be effective upon assumption or upon return from official leave of absence, scholarship or training, shall be exempt from this provision</list_item>
</unordered_list>
